title: Complete Trance Collection
description:
This is my first Torrent, so take it easy on me!
I compiled a huge collection of Cd&#039;s I had and Mp3&#039;s I had downloaded so You guys could benefit from having all the best trance songs all in one collection. 

Albums included are:

ATC - Planet Pop
BT - Emotional Technology
DJ Encore - Intuition
Paul Oakenfold - A Voyage Into Trance
Paul Oakenfold - Perfecto Presents Another World (Disc 2)
Paul Van Dyk - Global
Paul Van Dyk - Out There And Back (Disc 2)
Sasha - Global Underground: Ibiza 013
World&#039;s Greatest Euphoric Trance
Anthems of Ibiza (2004)
Best of Trance, Vol.4
Trance Classics
Wild Trance Anthems
